# Task 18 – Innovation

## Project

Smart Library Request Workflow in ServiceNow

## Description

This task highlights the innovative features implemented to improve automation, usability, security, and scalability within the Smart Library Request Workflow application.

## Innovations Implemented

- End-to-End Automation using Flow Designer
- Optimized Book Selection using Reference Qualifiers
- Maintainable and Scalable design using ServiceNow out-of-the-box features
- Dynamic UI using UI Policies
- Role-Based Security using ACLs
- Automated reporting for library insights

## Benefits

- Reduced manual work
- Faster approvals
- Improved data accuracy
- Better user experience
- Easy future enhancements
- Secure access control

## Technologies Used

- ServiceNow
- Flow Designer
- UI Policies
- Access Control Lists (ACLs)
- Reference Qualifiers
- Reports

## Status

Completed
